Utterance.UttText: Rob Mahe, 62 years old under Dr Jaime, came in for allergy tests and asthma experiments and for physio.
He has multiple allergies and he's got history of asthma.
He had rash from the allergy test, he wasn't happy about it and his physiotherapist said his meds needs adjustment.
He is to be discharged today though.
He is all ready to go.
His discharge papers is already been done and He is just waiting for his tablets.
